title: Closer Cooperation Between Russia, Europe Would Be 'Disaster' for US
text: Austrian Legal Expert Monika Donner proves that there are people who work for Western authorities, ministries and the military, but have an alternative point of view. People working for such structures have a deeper insight, but very few of them are ready to risk their careers and share their views publicly. ...
